ox-sizing: inherit; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 40px; position: relative; counter-reset: custom-counter 0; list-style: none; color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 8px;\">It’s just mind-blowingly awesome. I apologize, and I wish I was more articulate, but it’s hard to be articulate when your mind’s blown—but in a very good way.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 8px;\">The vehicle explodes, literally explodes, off the pad. The simulator shakes you a little bit, but the actual liftoff shakes your entire body and soul.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 8px;\">The surface is fine and powdery. I can kick it up loosely with my toe.</li></ol><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 25px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The vehicle explodes, literally explodes, off the pad. The simulator shakes you a little bit, but the actual liftoff shakes your entire body and soul.</p><h2 id=\"the-future\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-size: 2.6rem; line-height: normal; padding-top: 30px; margin-top: 45px; border-top: 1px solid var(--be-divider-default); color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\">The Future</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 25px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">I am a stranger. I come in peace. Take me to your leader and there will be a massive reward for you in eternity.</p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-left: 5px solid var(--be-divider-default); padding: 3px 30px 7px 20px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 35px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-word;\">Houston, that may have seemed like a very long final phase. The autotargeting was taking us right into a … crater, with a large number of big boulders and rocks … and it required … flying manually over the rock field to find a reasonably good area.I saw for the first time the earth’s shape. I could easily see the shores of continents, islands, great rivers, folds of the terrain, large bodies of water. The horizon is dark blue, smoothly turning to black. . . the feelings which filled me I can express with one word—joy.</p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 25px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Our posturings, our imagined self-importance, the delusion that we have some privileged position in the Universe, are challenged by this point of pale light. Our planet is a lonely speck in the great enveloping cosmic dark. In our obscurity, in all this vastness, there is no hint that help will come from elsewhere to save us from ourselves.</p><div class=\"widget widget-info widget-important\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 237); max-width: 100%; padding: 14px; margin: 35px 0px; border-radius: 3px; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-left: 5px solid rgb(243, 161, 44); font-size: 1.7rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(67, 72, 77);\">Important:</div>There is perhaps no better demonstration of the folly of human conceits than this distant image of our tiny world.</div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">From this day forward, Flight Control will be known by two words: ‘Tough’ and ‘Competent.’ Tough means we are forever accountable for what we do or what we fail to do. We will never again compromise our responsibilities. Every time we walk into Mission Control we will know what we stand for. Competent means we will never take anything for granted. We will never be found short in our knowledge and in our skills. Mission Control will be perfect. When you leave this meeting today you will go to your office and the first thing you will do there is to write ‘Tough and Competent’ on your blackboards. It will never be erased. Each day when you enter the room these words will remind you of the price paid by Grissom, White, and Chaffee. These words are the price of admission to the ranks of Mission Control.</span></p><h2 id=\"whats-next\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-size: 2.6rem; line-height: normal; padding-top: 30px; margin-top: 45px; border-top: 1px solid var(--be-divider-default); color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\">What\'s Next</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 25px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">It has been said that astronomy is a humbling and character-building experience. There is perhaps no better demonstration of the folly of human conceits than this distant image of our tiny world.</p><div class=\"widget widget-info\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(243, 251, 247); max-width: 100%; padding: 14px; margin: 35px 0px; border-radius: 3px; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-left: 5px solid rgb(90, 200, 145); font-size: 1.7rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(67, 72, 77);\">Note:</div>To me, it underscores our responsibility to deal more kindly with one another, and to preserve and cherish the pale blue dot, the only home we’ve ever known.</div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 72, 77); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The Earth is a very small stage in a vast cosmic arena.</span><br></p>', '7', '2', '1', '0', 'documentation,future,use', '2021-06-23 10:34:58', '2021-06-23 10:34:58');
