INSERT INTO `knowledge` VALUES ('6', 'Can I attach files to forms?', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">One of the key things that webmasters around the world look for in a CMS is versatility. When it comes to versatility, Joomla CMS is better than all its competitors. Joomla Customization Services act as the greatest USP for Joomla development. In todays highly competitive cyber space, having a unique look and feel to your website or blog is a must and Joomla developers can create unique features in your website with the use of Joomla customization services. This will allow you to be an instant hit on the web and add a competitive advantage to your website.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Joomla developers are widely using Joomla customization services in developing small business, corporate, educational, and religious websites. What s more, Joomla customization services can be used to build highly interactive websites such as social networking sites, polling websites, e-commerce enabled websites, image galleries and many more. Dont be surprised if you come to know that some of the biggest corporate houses in the world run their websites run using Joomla CMS. In other words Joomla customization services add an edge to Joomla development.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">What Can You Do with Joomla customization services</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">You can go for custom development of the existing Joomla templates with the use of Joomla customization services. This will help you in making your website look different from others using the same template.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Joomla developers can build and manage search-engine friendly websites with special access features for users, which helps in increasing the traffic and revenue earned by your website.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">In Joomla development, these services can help you build and manage business directories and shopping carts. You can also customize distribution of e-mails, newsletters and maintain public forums.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Joomla customization services allow you to develop communication systems, product catalogs, and inventory control and management systems.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Managing advertising on your website becomes easy with Joomla customization services. You can easily manage side banners or advertisements on your web pages. Advertisement of different sizes and formats can be managed. Apart from this you can also create custom headers and footers for your website.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Where to Get It Done</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">One of the biggest pluses for Joomla development is the fact that there are many offshore development centers engaged in custom development of websites using the Joomla CMS. These agencies let you hire experienced Joomla developers to build you unique websites. When you outsource your Joomla development to these offshore development centers, they not only provide you with expertise but also give you a cost advantage. It always makes business sense to hire Joomla developers based on the need of your project rather than hiring them directly on your payrolls.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">The flexibility that Joomla customization services add to your Joomla development is immense. You will be able to apply quick solutions for all your business needs using these customization services.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 64, 71); font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Our website link:- http://www.evontech.com/joomla-development.html</span><br></p>', '7', '3', '1', '0', 'joomla,customization', '2021-06-23 10:39:15', '2021-07-04 10:12:47');

